title: Elzeitra, Trendstress of the Dark 3/16: The Bachelor, Prince Philip, North Korea, Movie Pass, Dan Bongino, Jared Kushner
itunes:title: Elzeitra, Trendstress of the Dark 3/16: The Bachelor, Prince Philip, North Korea, Movie Pass, Dan Bongino, Jared Kushner
description:
On this edition of Elzeitra, Trendstress of the Dark Jack, Miles, and Anna Hossnieh discuss the Bachelor choosing a winner, then dumping her in season finale, Prince Philip leaving hospital following heart surgery, North Korea warning Biden not to "cause a stink", Movie Pass teasing relaunch, Dan Bongino thinks losing anti-defamation lawsuit is a "Big Win", and Jared Kushner leaves tax payers with $24,000 hotel tab.
